### Summary of Git Diff (HEAD~4..HEAD)

The last 4 commits wrapped several bare functions (`handleMyOrders`, `handleGoBack`, `handlerGoHome`, `handleApiErrorPress`) in `useCallback`, added exhaustive dependencies to the mount `useEffect` (`requestInitialData`, `clear`), and added previously-missing dependencies to the `useMemo` for `view`. These changes were correctness improvements, but they introduced a new dependency chain that needs scrutiny.

